#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kappname; is a ship sinking game for &kde;. Ships are placed on a board "
#| "which represents the sea. Players try to hit each others ships in turns "
#| "without knowing where they are placed. The first player to destroy all "
#| "ships wins the game."
msgid ""
"&i18n-knavalbattle; is a ship sinking game by &kde;. Ships are placed on a "
"board which represents the sea. Players try to hit each others ships in "
"turns without knowing where they are placed. The first player to destroy all "
"ships wins the game."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; je igra potapanja brodova &kde;. Brodovi su smješteni na ploču "
"koja predstavlja more. Igrači pokušavaju pogoditi brodove jedan drugom "
"naizmjenično bez prethodnog znanja gdje se oni nalaze. Prvi igrač koji "
"uništi sve brodove je pobjednik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Uputstva za igranje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sink all of the opponent’s ships before the opponent sink all the ships of "
"your own."
msgstr ""
"Potopi sve brodove protivnika prije nego protivnik potopi sve tvoje brodove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you want to play &kappname;, you will need two players, either play "
#| "against the computer or in a network against another player. To play "
#| "against your computer, first select the difficulty level on the right of "
#| "the status bar, and then select <guibutton>Single Player</guibutton> on "
#| "the welcome screen, or directly on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
#| "guimenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgid ""
"If you want to play &i18n-knavalbattle;, you will need two players, either "
"play against the computer or in a network against another player. To play "
"against your computer, first select the difficulty level on the right of the "
"status bar, and then select <guilabel>Single Player</guilabel> on the "
"welcome screen, or directly on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Single Player</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Ukoliko želite igradi &kappname;, trebat će vam 2 igrača, igrajte ili protiv "
"računara ili na internetu protiv drugog igrača. Da biste igrali protiv svog "
"računara, prvo odaberite nivo težine desno od statusne trake, a zatim "
"izaberite <guibutton>Jedan igrač</guibutton> na početnom zaslonu, ili "
"direktno na <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu></menuchoice> meni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To start a network game, one player has to host the game by selecting "
#| "<guilabel>Host Network Game</guilabel> on the welcome screen, or choosing "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Host Game...</"
#| "guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A dialog box opens which asks for a "
#| "<guilabel>Nickname:</guilabel> and <guilabel>Port:</guilabel>. Normally, "
#| "&kappname; will suggest your full name, but you can enter any string you "
#| "want. The predefined port should be ok. However, if you encounter "
#| "problems, you can choose any other free port above 1024."
msgid ""
"To start a network game, one player has to host the game by selecting "
"<guilabel>Host Network Game</guilabel> on the welcome screen, or choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Host Game…</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. A dialog box opens which asks for a <guilabel>Nickname:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Port:</guilabel>. Normally, &i18n-knavalbattle; will "
"suggest your full name, but you can enter any string you want. The "
"predefined port should be ok. However, if you encounter problems, you can "
"choose any other free port above 1024."
msgstr ""
"Da biste započeli igru na internetu, jedan igrač treba da bude domaćin igre "
"tako što odabere <guilabel>Budi domaćin igre</guilabel> na početnom zaslonu, "
"ili odabirom <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Budi domaćin..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Otvorit će se dijalog u koji trebate upisati "
"<guilabel>Nadimak:</guilabel> i <guilabel>Port:</guilabel>. Obično, "
"&kappname; će sugerirati vaše puno ime, ali možete upisati string koji "
"hoćete. Prvobitno definisani port bi trebao biti ok. Međutim, ukoliko "
"naiđete na problem, možete izabrati bilo koji slobodan port iznad 1024."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You need to tell the other player in case you use a port other than the "
"default as both players need to use the same port in order to be able to "
"establish a connection."
msgstr ""
"Trebate reći drugom igraču koji port koristite u slučaju da koristite port "
"koji nije zadani jer oba igrača moraju koristiti isti port da bi ostvarili "
"konekciju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The other player has to choose <guilabel>Connect to Network Game</"
#| "guilabel>, or click <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Connect to Game...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Again, a "
#| "<guilabel>Nickname:</guilabel> is suggested, but you can choose any name "
#| "you like. In the field <guilabel>Hostname:</guilabel> you have to enter "
#| "the host name of the server (the machine of the player that initiated the "
#| "game)."
msgid ""
"The other player has to choose <guilabel>Connect to Network Game</guilabel>, "
"or click on the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Connect to "
"Game…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Again, a <guilabel>Nickname:</"
"guilabel> is suggested, but you can choose any nickname you like. In the "
"field <guilabel>Hostname:</guilabel> you have to enter the host name of the "
"server (the machine of the player that initiated the game)."
msgstr ""
"Drugi igrač treba odabrati <guilabel>Spoji se na mrežnu igru</guilabel>, ili "
"kliknuti <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spoji se na igru..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Opet, <guilabel>Nadimak:</guilabel> je "
"sugeriran, ali možete izabrati bilo koje ime. U polje <guilabel>Ime Domaćina:"
"</guilabel> trebate upisati ime servera domaćina (mašine igrača koji je "
"započeo igru)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done, you can start the game. Simply follow the instructions in "
"the statusbar. It will issue hints and suggest what to do next. When you now "
"look at the screen, you will find two grid fields, the so-called "
"<quote>battle areas</quote>. The left area belongs to you. This is where you "
"place your ships and where you can follow the military actions of your "
"enemy. The right area is where your enemy's fleet is located. When it's your "
"turn to fire, you need to click on a certain sector (a field of the battle "
"area) where you suppose the ships to be located."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste završili, možete započeti igru. Jednostavno pratite instrukcije u "
"statusnoj traci. Prikazivat će upute i sugerisati sljedeće poteze. Sada kada "
"pogledate na zaslon, vidjet ćete dva polja sa rešetkom, takozvano "
"<quote>područje borbe</quote>. Lijeva površina pripada vama. Ovdje postavite "
"svoje brodove i možete pratiti napade protivnika. Na desnoj površini se "
"nalazi flota vašeg protivnika. Kada je vaš red za napad, trebate kliknuti na "
"određeno polje na površini protivnika gdje pretpostavljate da bi se brodovi "
"mogao nalaziti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you need to place your ships. The game initiator starts. When he/she "
"is done, player two sets his/her ships."
msgstr ""
"Prvo, trebate postaviti svoje brodove.  Inicijator igre počinje. Kad on/ona "
"završi, igrač dva postavlja svoje brodove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ship placement is very easy: simply click on the field where you want to "
"place your ships. You have four ships to place: the first one will have a "
"length of one square, the next will be two squares long &etc; Click on the "
"field where you want to start the placement. By default, ships will be "
"placed horizontally; to rotate them 90 degrees, click the &RMB; before the "
"placement."
msgstr ""
"Postavljanje brodova je veoma lako: jednostano kliknite na polje na koje "
"želite postaviti svoj brod. Trebate smjestiti četiri broda: prvi je dužine "
"jedne kocke, sljedeći dužine 2 kocke &etc; Kliknite na polje gdje želite "
"započeti smještanje. Zadani način smještanja je horizontalno; da biste ih "
"rotirali za 90 stepeni, kliknite &RMB; prije smještanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a ship is hit, fire will break out on it. To sink it, hit all the "
"squares it occupies. A sunk ship will appear faded."
msgstr ""
"Kada je brod pogođen, pojavit će se vatra na njemu. Da biste ga potopili, "
"trebate pogoditi sva polja koja zauzima. Nakon potapanja, brod će "
"izblijediti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can use the &LMB; to fire on the battle area of your enemy. The "
"status bar indicates who is about to shoot."
msgstr ""
"Sada možete koristiti &LMB; da napadnete područje na kojem je vaš "
"neprijatelj. Statusna traka pokazuje ko će napasti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can restart the game by choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Restart Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or by pressing "
#| "<keycap>F5</keycap>."
msgid ""
"You can restart the game by choosing the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Restart Game</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item, or by "
"pressing <keycap>F5</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Možete restartoavti igru odabirom <menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Restartuj igru</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ili pritiskom na "
"tipku <keycap>F5</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The first player to destroy all their opponents ships wins the game."
msgid "The first player to destroy all their opponent's ships wins the game."
msgstr "Prvi igrač koji potopi sve brodove protivnika je pobjednik igre."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, Strategije i savjeti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "A player can only fire one shot per turn."
msgstr "Igrač može samo jednom gađati kada je na redu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players must place all their ships."
msgstr "Igrači moraju postaviti sve svoje brodove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot be moved once placed."
msgstr "Brodovi se ne mogu pomjerati nakon što su jednom postavljeni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "A ship is sunk when all the squares it occupies are hit."
msgstr "Brod je potopljen kada su pogođena sva polja koja on zauzima."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije i savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Never place ships next to one another."
msgstr "Nikada nemojte stavljati brodove jedan pored drugoga."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Once you hit a ship, try shooting around the place you hit."
msgstr ""
"Kada jednom pogodite brod, pokušajte gađati polja oko mjesta gdje ste "
"pogodili brod."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try to place ships away from the edges of the board."
msgstr "Pokušajte postavljati brodove dalje od ivica vašeg područja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Small ships are harder to hit, make sure you place them where they are hard "
"to find."
msgstr ""
"Mali brodovi su teži za pogoditi, potrudite se da ih postavite negdje gdje "
"ih je teško naći."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Think before you shoot. Hits on water gives less points."
msgstr "Razmislite prije nego što gađate. Pogađanje vode donosi manje poena."

